Package domain

Class Token

java.lang.Object
domain.Token
All Implemented Interfaces:
PlayToken, Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
HeavyToken, NormalToken, OverlapToken, TemporaryToken
public abstract class Token extends Object implements PlayToken, Serializable
The Token class is an abstract class representing a generic game token in a Gomoku game. It serves as the base class for various token types and provides common attributes and methods. Subclasses of Token define specific behaviors for different types of tokens.
Version:
1.8.5
Author:
Juan Daniel Murcia - Mateo Forero Fuentes
